{
  "stem": "19502.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 167.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they came from the Judenrat and they say today we want so much silver.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So whatever we had, we gather from house to house, whatever we had in the house.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If we had a goblet, or we have spoons, cutlery, anything, we gathered.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we gave.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't understand that time, but it's almost like buying a day of life.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, now, when I look at it, I knew.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But that how it-- it was that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Judenrat were wonderful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, they-- they-- the German, you know, the burgomeister, whatever, came.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know if it's burgomeister.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I know from the army, came to them, and they approached us, you see.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was a man, [NON-ENGLISH], and he couldn't take it no more.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He committed suicide.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He couldn't-- he felt that he is selling out the-- the-- the-- the-- the town.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was the head of the-- it, you know, and then [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Broder ?] came up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no rumors.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There's nothing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't hear a thing about any killing, about what was going on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't know what was going on at the next town.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't know--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in 1942, because my father was killed in '41.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had a very severe winter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't have woods to heat the-- the-- the-- the-- the-- our-- our houses were heated with-- with wood, you know.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, so primitive and so on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when-- when-- when it-- when it came the first year, you know, it-- it was-- it was hard to-- to explain.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You weren't a person.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And somehow, I don't know why I was a child, but I constantly kept crying.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't know why.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I says, I want my father.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I want my father.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't know why.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
